    "Future work could focus on hybrid approaches, combining RL with other ML techniques, to enhance scalability and efficiency.",
    "This paper presents a dynamic, ML-based solution for resource allocation in ERP systems, leveraging reinforcement learning to address limitations of traditional approaches.",
